description:
This is a 18 minute workout called '10 Minute Morning Breathwork Routine To Start Your Day Anxiety Free' from the channel Breathe With Sandy.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Breathe away all anxiety and worry about your day in just 10 minutes. This guided breathwork session is designed to help you start your day anxiety-free and full of energy. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned breathworker, this simple breathing technique will enhance your mental clarity, reduce stress, and improve your overall well being. Perfect for anyone looking to transform their morning routine into a source of calm and vitality.
